<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=100653062791190></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f100653062791190><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=?class=4&mid=100653062791190>Strategy for lvl 27 to 40 bard solo :)</a> <a id=fs8 href=?class=4&mid=100653062791190#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=20 width=20></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=121686><span id= >Noirac</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>2 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Nov 23rd 10:50 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello!<br>Here is my hunting guide for bards who wants to solo from lvl 27 to 40 :)<br>Excuse my english if there are some mistakes because I am french...<br>I ve already post strategy for lvl1 to 17 and 17 to 27..send me an e-mail at valaba.noirac@caramail.com I will send them to you ;)<br>Leveling from 27 to 40 as a bard :<br>_ From lvl 27 to 31 : A very good place is Lake of Ill Omen, go to the west of the lake in the zone (opposite from the ruins) where there are 2 pillars going out of the water, it will be your hunting place until 31. For these lvls you just need 3 songs : Selo's Consonant Chain (23), Angstlich's Appalling Screech fear (26), and Jonathan's Whistling Warsong (7) ; put them in this order in your hotkeys (1,2,3) and in 4 i put BBB, in 5 Hymn of resto and in 6 selo. Stay near the shore and pull 1 mob at a time (I pull with chain), slow him then fear then haste : you will see if your brass skill is maxed (for fear) this technique give incredible fast xp ! no downtime ! (I just loose 1 or 2 bubbles max of hp per mob and sometime nothing...) ; just a tip ;) if you pull 2 or more mobs dont ask you questions, start selo and go to the frontier mountains zone wich is really near ! At 30 most of the mobs will still con blue : the hell lvl is going so fast ;), at 31 kill some mobs still blue to get at least 1 or 2 bubbles of xp.<br>_ From lvl 31 to 34 : Go to South Karana and head towards paw, try to get one of the middle or north spires (hill is good too) and use the same technique with the tesh mash gnolls (good loot and money) at 34 i can take 2 or 3 at a time : slow one and fear the all group it is working good ;), if you have some trouble go zone inside paw ! (it is always better to loose a kill than to be killed...). If you find a group you can go inside paw but the xp will be not as fast as if you stay alone.<br>_ At 35 hell lvl again... ;) : go to upper Guk to the ancient and saltwater crocs, the respawn time is 16 min, they spawn from 1 to 5 at a time. You can solo them easely with Anthem, BBB, DDD, heal and chain. They are incredible xp! you will loot almost nothing (rarely some runes or words)...Except when you get the luck that the AC (ancient croc) spawn! Dont ask for help! you can kite him easely!: when facing him stay close to the right or left wall, chain him then BBB and Fulfil, here is the part: dont stop going up and down the stairs! the AC is going up and down only in the middle so if you keep right or left he wont ever hit you! and you ll get the loot gatorscale leggings or sleeves (selling for 500pp).<br>_ From 36 to 40 : I hunt in a really not well known place Stonebrunt mountains ! This new zone is dangerous but is also incredible for the nice quests you can do at these lvls and all the mobs who con blue from 36 to 40 ! like we have now track skill it is easy to find pandas (for claws) and invaders heretics (for heads) ; from these lvl I made 4 times the quest of the wakizashi of the frozen skies (<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=6655" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=6655</a>) and 1 time the heretics head quest (got the headband ;( ) (<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=1281" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=1281</a>) , try to kill as much pandas as you can to get claws like tigers skin are really easy to get, for asp poison just to Oasis and kill cistern asp....at least 12 asp poison in 20 min ;)<br>You will reach lvl40 rapidly ;)<br>Good luck to you all !<br><br>Valaba Noirac<br>40 Bard on Therris Thulle<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
