	   <tr><td colspan=2>ok after you scribe the song, you should be able to see little dents to your left hand side, there should be eight of them. now right click on the song till a bubble pops up on the cursor. Now drag it over to one of the dents and right click again till it dissapears and a red bar to the right of the meditate button appears, wait till its finished and Boom you gots yourself a song.<br><br><br>-Duuo Doowahdiddy<br>-28 bard on Innoruuk.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
